            <mo>=3D</mo>
            <mn>1</mn>
          </mrow>
          <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>n</mi>
          </mrow>
        </munderover>
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <msubsup>
            <mi>w</mi>
            <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
              <mi>i</mi>
            </mrow>
            <mo>=E2=80=B2</mo>
          </msubsup>
        </mrow>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mn>1</mn>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\textstyle \sum \limits _{i=
=3D1}^{n}{w_{i}'}=3D1}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/6de1f80786c0ae3626aa3dd9ccc570a0cbbe9e5f" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -2.505ex; width:9.78ex; height:6.009ex;" alt=3D"{\textstyle \sum \l=
imits _{i=3D1}^{n}{w_{i}'}=3D1}"></span>.
For such normalized weights, the weighted mean is equivalently:
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
s=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyl=
e {\bar {x}}=3D\sum \limits _{i=3D1}^{n}{w_{i}'x_{i}}}">
