</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/53a5c55e536acf250c1d3e0f754be5692b843ef5" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.338ex; width:2.385ex; height:2.676ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle \si=
gma ^{2}}"></span>, the <i>standard error of the weighted mean</i>, <span c=
lass=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-m=
athml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"=
http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyle \sigma _{\bar=
 {x}}}">
