.org/wiki/Uncertainty_propagation" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Uncertain=
ty propagation">uncertainty propagation</a> to be:
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
s=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\textstyle \=
sigma _{\bar {x}}=3D\sigma {\sqrt {\sum \limits _{i=3D1}^{n}w_{i}'^{2}}}}">
