ator</a> of the mean of the probability distributions under the assumption =
that they are independent and <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Norm=
ally_distributed" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Normally distributed">norm=
ally distributed</a> with the same mean.
</p>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id=3D"Statistical_properties">Sta=
tistical properties</h2><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-ed=
