<p>The weighted sample mean, <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-eleme=
nt-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" styl=
e=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alt=
