</p>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Weighted_sample_covariance"=
>Weighted sample covariance</h3><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=
=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/i=
ndex.php?title=3DWeighted_arithmetic_mean&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D2=
0" title=3D"Edit section: Weighted sample covariance"><span>edit</span></a>=
<span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>In a weighted sample, each row vector <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mw=
e-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathm=
l-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math=
/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyle \mathbf {x} _{i}}">
