</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/5bc4e26452494d1471216374f94480d6cd17173e" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.671ex; width:6.725ex; height:2.509ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle w_{=
i}\geq 0}"></span>.
</p><p>Then the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Weighted_mean" cla=
ss=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Weighted mean">weighted mean</a> vector <span c=
lass=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-m=
athml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"=
