i=3D1}^{N}w_{i}}}.}"></span></dd></dl>
<p>And the weighted covariance matrix is given by:<sup id=3D"cite_ref-PRICE=
-1972_9-0" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wei=
ghted_arithmetic_mean#cite_note-PRICE-1972-9"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">=
