      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle V_{1}=3D\sum =
_{i=3D1}^{N}w_{i}=3D1.}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/1211b25661626963192baa6ee056fa45790a20ce" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -3.005ex; width:16.622ex; height:7.343ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle V_=
{1}=3D\sum _{i=3D1}^{N}w_{i}=3D1.}"></span></dd></dl>
<p>(If they are not, divide the weights by their sum to normalize prior to =
