<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Weighted_averages_of_functi=
ons">Weighted averages of functions</h3><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><spa=
n class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.=
